Class DecodeServlet

java.lang.Object
jakarta.servlet.GenericServlet
jakarta.servlet.http.HttpServlet
com.google.zxing.web.DecodeServlet
All Implemented Interfaces:
jakarta.servlet.Servlet, jakarta.servlet.ServletConfig, Serializable
@WebServlet(value="/w/decode",loadOnStartup=1,initParams={@WebInitParam(name="maxAccessPerTime",value="120"),@WebInitParam(name="accessTimeSec",value="120"),@WebInitParam(name="maxEntries",value="100000")}) public final class DecodeServlet extends jakarta.servlet.http.HttpServlet
HttpServlet which decodes images containing barcodes. Given a URL, it will retrieve the image and decode it. It can also process image files uploaded via POST.
